property.description: Welcome to your own slice of Alaskan paradise! This breathtaking property along Chena Hot Springs Road spans over 5 acres and features a cozy yet spacious yurt, a newer dry cabin, and a charming barn. Previously a successful bed and breakfast and tour company specializing in dog mushing and aurora viewing, this property holds great potential for continued business ventures or personal use.The main home offers a delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom layout filled with warm living spaces and an abundance of natural light. Stay warm during those chilly Alaskan winters with the comforting wood stove. The real treasure of this property lies in its expansive outdoor space. The yurt and dry cabin provide versatile additional living areas, perfect for extended family visits, guest accommodations, or vacation rentals. The barn offers ample storage for all your outdoor gear, and dog mushing enthusiasts will find the yard to be an ideal playground. Nestled near vast trails, this property is a dream come true for outdoor enthusiasts, with easy access to hiking, skiing, and dog mushing, all while being just a short 20-minute drive from town. Don't miss your chance to own this amazing piece of Alaska! The property is sold strictly as-is, cash or renovation loan only. An appraisal from spring 2024 values the home at $290,000, and inspections are available upon request. Schedule your showing today before this incredible opportunity slips away!  Agent remarks (con't): Conexes available with acceptable offer.
